'''Diamond grinding''' is a [[Grinding (abrasive cutting)|grinding]] process that can be applied to a variety of surfaces including floors, stones and engineering ceramics.  It takes advantage of the fact that [[diamond]] has the highest [[hardness]] of any bulk material.

